  "code": "%%{IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}}}%%\n\nstateDiagram-v2\n  [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode] --> OFF\n  %% 시작 경로\n  OFF --> WARMUP: START(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker) + MODE=WARM_UP\n  OFF --> INIT: START(IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController)\n  INIT --> PRECOOL: init_seconds elapsed\n  PRECOOL --> RUN: T5 <= TSP - precool_band\n  %% READY 표출 (IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n  INIT --> READY: ready flag true\n  PRECOOL --> READY: ready flag true\n  RUN --> READY: ready flag true\n  READY --> RUN: ready flag cleared\n  %% 보류/재개\n  RUN --> HOLD: HOLD(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\n  READY --> HOLD: HOLD(IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n  HOLD --> RUN: RESUME(IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController)\n  %% 정지/전원 OFF\n  any --> OFF: STOP(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic) or OFF(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\n  WARMUP --> OFF: warm reached\n  %% 안전 전이\n  state SAFE_SHUTDOWN\n  INIT --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  PRECOOL --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  RUN --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  READY --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  HOLD --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  WARMUP --> SAFE_SHUTDOWN: Safety\n  SAFE_SHUTDOWN --> OFF: RESET(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)=ACK_ALARM\n",
