      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个典型的工业IoT场景。我理解为边缘节点初始状态应该是OFF，然后通过不同的启动路径进入工作状态。需要区分WARMUP和INIT两条启动路径吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "START"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，WARMUP是通过MQTT broker触发的系统预热，带MODE=WARM_UP参数；INIT是直接由执行器控制器本地启动的初始化流程。两条路径最终都要能进入运行态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "MODE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把OFF到WARMUP、OFF到INIT的转换画出来。INIT之后应该有个时间延迟吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OFF",
        "WARMUP",
        "INIT",
        "START"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "INIT完成后进入PRECOOL预冷状态，条件是init_seconds超时。然后PRECOOL到RUN的转换需要判断温度条件T5 <= TSP - precool_band，这是关键的控制逻辑。",
